N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4812.4 - Time when copies must be received by commission

State Regulations

One copy of the "Findings and Determination for Bingo

License" together with two copies of the application must be received by the
commission at least five days prior to the holding of the first game
authorized. Notes
